title: Re: Thank you for your bug report
source.subject: Re: Thank you for your bug report
source.body:
On Wed, Jan 10, 2024, 12:20 AM Civo <hello@civo.com> wrote:
Thank you for your bug bounty submission
Thank you for your bug bounty submission
We've received your report and will be in touch
Thank you for your bug bounty submission. Here is a summary of what we've received.
Bug Short Description:
No Rate Limit
Bug Description:
Summary: No rate limit check on resend verification link which can lead to mass mailing and spamming of users and possible employees A little bit about Rate Limit: A rate limiting algorithm is used to check if the user session (or IP-address) has to be limited based on the information in the session cache.
Exact Steps to Replicate:
Steps To Reproduce The Issue 1- create account and go to resend verification link 2- intercept burp and send request to intruder 3- make payload and start attack Suggested fix Use CAPTCHA verification if many request sent. Impact 1- Attacker could use this vulnerability to bomb out the email inbox of the victim. 2- Attacker could send Spear-Phishing to the selected mail address. similar reports :::: 1-https://hackerone.com/reports/751604 2-https://hackerone.com/reports/441161
If you have any questions, please don't hesitate to contact us.
Your Civo team
© 2024 Civo.com
Civo Ltd, Units H-K, Gateway 1000, Whittle Way, Stevenage, Hertfordshire, SG1 2FP, United Kingdom
source.author.name: Gaurav Shukla

title: Thought Leadership Opportunity: Proposing a Guest Post for Your Blog
source.subject: Thought Leadership Opportunity: Proposing a Guest Post for Your Blog
source.body:
Hello,


I hope you are doing well.I am reaching out today because I would love to contribute a guest post to your website.I have been an avid reader of your website for some time now and have always been impressed by the quality of your content.


I believe that I can add value to your website by providing a guest post on a topic that I think your readers would find interesting.


I understand that you may receive many guest post pitches, so I want to assure you that my post will be well-researched, original, and in line with your website's standards and guidelines. If you're interested, I would be happy to provide a draft of the post for your review.


Thank you for considering my proposal, and I look forward to hearing from you soon.


Best regards,

Joshua
